## 1. WHAT INFORMATION DO WE COLLECT?

**Personal Information you disclose to us**

**In Short:** We collect personal information that you provide to us.

- Name  
- Phone number  
- Email address

We do **not** process **sensitive** information. Please ensure the data is complete, true, and accurate.

---

## 2. HOW DO WE PROCESS YOUR INFORMATION?

**In Short:** To provide, improve, and administer our services; communicate with you; for fraud prevention; and comply with law.

We process your info for purposes such as:

- Responding to support/inquiries  
- Requesting feedback  
- Delivering targeted ads or personalized content (if applicable)

---

## 3. WHEN AND WITH WHOM DO WE SHARE YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION?

**In Short:** Only in specific cases such as:

- **Business Transfers** – e.g. mergers, acquisitions, or asset sales

---

## 4. WHAT IS OUR STANCE ON THIRD-PARTY WEBSITES?

**In Short:** We are not responsible for third-party content or privacy policies.  
Our app may link to external services or sites. Interact with them at your own risk.

---

## 5. HOW LONG DO WE KEEP YOUR INFORMATION?

**In Short:** As long as necessary for outlined purposes or legal obligations.  
Once no longer needed, we **delete** or **anonymize** your info.

---

## 6. DO WE COLLECT INFORMATION FROM MINORS?

**In Short:** No. We don’t knowingly collect or market to users under 18.  
If discovered, we will delete the data and deactivate the account.

---

## 7. WHAT ARE YOUR PRIVACY RIGHTS?

**In Short:** You can review, change, or terminate your account at any time.  
You may withdraw your consent at any time by contacting us at [wenyafi@gmail.com](mailto:wenyafi@gmail.com)

---

## 8. CONTROLS FOR DO-NOT-TRACK FEATURES

We don’t currently support “Do-Not-Track” (DNT) signals due to lack of a standard.  
If this changes, we’ll update this notice accordingly.

---

## 9. DO OTHER REGIONS HAVE SPECIFIC PRIVACY RIGHTS?

### Australia & New Zealand

Compliant with **Privacy Act 1988** (AU) and **Privacy Act 2020** (NZ).  
You can access, correct, or delete your data anytime.

Contacts:

- [Office of Australian Information Commissioner](https://www.oaic.gov.au)  
- [Office of NZ Privacy Commissioner](https://www.privacy.org.nz)

### Republic of South Africa

Compliant with **POPIA**.  
For complaints:

- General: [enquiries@inforegulator.org.za](mailto:enquiries@inforegulator.org.za)  
- Complaints:  
  [PAIAComplaints@inforegulator.org.za](mailto:PAIAComplaints@inforegulator.org.za)  
  [POPIAComplaints@inforegulator.org.za](mailto:POPIAComplaints@inforegulator.org.za)

---

